plan error: LogicalPlanError: Query planning error: size([x IN list WHERE (pattern)]) where the pattern has no correlation to an outer variable (it references only the iteration variable) is not yet supported — the count would silently drop the pattern predicate and return a plain row count (#612). Workaround: correlate the pattern to an outer variable, or express the constrained count via a top-level MATCH ... WHERE ... WITH count(...).